songs.title: The Way You Look
songs.lyrics:
[Verse: Normani]
All the things that you said
Shouldn't listen
Knew this bae wasn’t far in the distance

[Pre-Chorus: Camila]
There she comes from [?]
Wanna caught your heart
I'll be nice and say hello
But it's so hard

[Chorus: Lauren]
You don’t look at me
The way you look at her
Always thought that I would be
The one for ya'
Everything she's given you
Should give to me
I don't know what else to do
To make you see

[Chorus: Lauren; Lauren and Camila; Ally]
You don't look at me
The way you look at her
Now I see you staring
At your new future
Something in her eyes
Gives you what you need
Thought that you would
See the same in me
Yeah﻿
